        "rationale": "Focuses on communication-first recovery in zone B during middle stage, with stagnation detection and material conservation. Revised state adds stagnation tracking and backbone progress indicators. Intrinsic reward prioritizes comm_B actions that improve backbone communication, penalizes wasteful actions, and provides anti-stagnation incentives when progress stalls.",
